Package Enginegames

Interface Tickable

All Known Implementing Classes:
Apple, Button, Deathscreen, Dialog, Head, Label, ScrollButton, Settingsscreen, Snakeworld, Textfield, Tile, World, WorldObj
public interface Tickable
an interface, which makes Classes able to be called every tick by an engine.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void _tick()
    the super methode, for ticking.
    void tick()
    function which gets called every tick for objects and worlds

  • Method Details

    • _tick

      void _tick()
      the super methode, for ticking. this is the one being called every tick. should be final and call the tick() method. This is a way to call functions in super classes without having to be manually called in the objects

    • tick

      void tick()
      function which gets called every tick for objects and worlds
